                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>My dear sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>\n                                        <date>Jany 31.'54</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">You were good enough to loan<lb/> me some years\n                                        ago “The Chronicles of<lb/>\n                                        <persName>Rabbi Joseph Ben Joshua Ben Meir</persName>,\n                                        the<lb/> Sph<add>?</add>”—translated by\n                                                  <persName>Bialloblotzky<add>?</add></persName>—<lb/>\n                                        I have lately added to my little collection<lb/> of Hebrew\n                                        matter a copy of the Original<lb/>\n                                        <add>Hebrew</add> and would like again to have<lb/> for a\n                                        while your vols: if you will do me<lb/> that favour I shall\n                                        be obliged to you—</p>\n                              <p>We have been expecting for some time<lb/> our copy of your Bible,\n                                        as we understand<lb/> that it was in the hands of\n                                                  <persName><add>?</add></persName><lb/> in\n                                                  <placeName>Phila</placeName>\n                                        <persName>Dr McCulloh</persName> has been long<lb/> anxious\n                                        for his—and <persName>Mr Lenaman</persName> also<lb/> wishes\n                                        a copy—so that when our turn<lb/> comes</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p32805j8g/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
